    Page: 5
    Verse: 17
Tags:
  - '6'
---
Dreaming has its place; inspiration is invaluable; but life is action as
well as thought. They get farthest in the realm of character-building who
link up thought and action, who do not merely dream, but act upon their
noblest imaginings.
